John Blyth Barrymore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Blyth_Barrymore 0 John Blyth Barrymore III (born May 15, 1954) is an American film and television actor. He is known for his role as Zeke in the 1970s television series Kung Fu, which was his first role on television.
